wiki.summary: ALL MY FELLAS is a track written and produced by Frizk in August 2023. He released a video featuring the track for his TikTok page not thinking that it would soon become one of the most recognizable viral meme songs in the world overnight. He then released the track on all platforms on September 19th, 2023 after an extreme burst of popularity and memes for this track. This repetitive, release-cut piano style is very similar to the track "Moonlight by Shiganai Koukousei". Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: ALL MY FELLAS is a track written and produced by Frizk in August 2023. He released a video featuring the track for his TikTok page not thinking that it would soon become one of the most recognizable viral meme songs in the world overnight. He then released the track on all platforms on September 19th, 2023 after an extreme burst of popularity and memes for this track. This repetitive, release-cut piano style is very similar to the track "Moonlight by Shiganai Koukousei". This track was not sampled in ALL MY FELLAS as Frizk stated in his YouTube video "How I made ALL MY FELLAS", even though they sound extremely similar. This video features Frizk talking to his audience and explaining what he did to make this track. ALL MY FELLAS reached #3 on most Shazamed tracks for the dance genre in October 2023.
